data.description: Exquisite 3-Bedroom, 2-Bathroom House with Bonus Room & Enclosed Patio! Are you ready to make your dreams come true in the heart of Orlando? Look no further! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home has a split floorplan and an open concept perfect for entertaining along with plenty of potential to make your own. The large lot is perfect for entertaining family and friends. Conveniently located near downtown Orlando you are minutes from the parks, shopping, and convenient access to all major roadways. New water heater & AC in 2018, new roof in 2020!
